  <brief_title>Low Frequency Deep Brain Stimulation of the Subthalamic Nucleus in Parkinson's Disease</brief_title>
  <official_title>Safety and Feasibility of Using Low Frequency Deep Brain Stimulation of the Subthalamic Nucleus to Improve Cognitive Performance in Patients With Parkinson's Disease</official_title>
  <sponsors>
